/span>, Erik Pot&scaron;inok (愛沙尼亞), Marlon D'Acunto (德國), Axel Ruski-Jones (紐西蘭), Hugo Galvez (法國), Sai Lake (澳洲), Luka Banek (克羅地亞)"},{"pid":"d3fdf302f868ad968ac02f673690b6441581db33","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T06:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3903ef928dbf29f8f461b487afcb6205bc70b90","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T09:30:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>年僅14歲代表香港出戰奧運 任遊：我三歲就開始打冰球</strong><br />\n<br />\n冬季青年奧運會（冬青奧）將於瑞士洛桑舉行，冰球小將任遊早前在全球選拔以第57名入圍，同時以14歲成為香港代表團中最年輕選手：「期望今次可以拎到牌，最希望梗係金牌啦！」能有如此自信，皆因他已在冰場馳騁11年，絕對是「冰場老將」。<br />\n<br />\n任遊三歲已與冰球結緣，全因他來自一個冰球世家：「我一開始係跟住阿哥打冰球，佢就同我舅父打波。」冰球允許合法碰撞，任遊起初亦不太習慣：「打冰球多碰撞，同埋細個唔識溜冰，成日都跌，嗰時覺得好辛苦。」不過，隨着他的技術越來越純熟，他漸漸享受在冰面上馳騁的速度而愛上冰球。<br />\n<br />\n冰球在歐美等地盛行，堪稱加拿大的國技，任遊曾經到當地體驗高水平賽事：「嗰陣10歲去加拿大一個訓練營，睇咗一場加拿大對美國嘅賽事，佢哋都係全球最頂級嘅冰球隊，比賽相當精采。」<br />\n<br />\n相反在香港打冰球的人僅以千計，絕對是冷門運動，任遊就希望今次與隊友徐綽希一同出戰冬青奧，可以令更多香港人認識冰球。"},{"pid":"4512260c2540e483a0e12d5a8ef4e54d0d4ab233","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c45921e9df0f886de88f7a76197227ffa8e942","tid":1810372,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"想比人炒20:0?"},{"pid":"719d61af38d6ae6234f702ed8fd54a010c90326d","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c45921e9df0f886de88f7a76197227ffa8e942","tid":1810372,"uid":104830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:04:40.000Z","msg":"想比人炒20:0?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T12:35:30.000Z","msg":"唔喺香港隊參加<br />\n佢兩個分開<br />\n隊友多數歐洲人"},{"pid":"2a19d8b3796c0c2c45b086fad95d8d8b7dd76e65","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VbTlsuRBfMg?t=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVbTlsuRBfMg%3Ft%3D4&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=348ea495\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VbTlsuRBfMg?t=4</a><br />\n幾年前呢個日本小朋友<br />\n練波段片全球都幾多人講<br />\n唔知有無份打奧運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d3af2c8c06a78c348849a55c042a5f41e6ce1ed","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T10:13:43.000Z","msg":"香港代表團今日出發去洛桑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119361974f5761389fcad4555da5d0fec540d8eb","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a19d8b3796c0c2c45b086fad95d8d8b7dd76e65","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T16:57:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VbTlsuRBfMg?t=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVbTlsuRBfMg%3Ft%3D4&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=348ea495\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VbTlsuRBfMg?t=4</a><br />\n幾年前呢個日本小朋友<br />\n練波段片全球都幾多人講<br />\n唔知有無份打奧運 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:30:04.000Z","msg":"原來佢叫井口藍仁<br />\n16歲就打緊u20世錦賽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b369caa55701d770779e808b1c2b90dd3c687c8c","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T15:30:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6d417ac8a72fd031e3dd230733428c328b7668","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:03:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O5McVUWoGxI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DO5McVUWoGxI&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDhVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=3724ba53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=O5McVUWoGxI</a><br />\n而家直播緊開幕禮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"554911337ec5206428aad47fa7078fa176a5b771","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:00:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzquVGQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzquVGQ.jpg&h=8139ca97&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dpG9VG1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdpG9VG1.jpg&h=2a7928aa&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UaigAG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUaigAG6.jpg&h=614e9f7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港代表團進場"},{"pid":"295a7bc8d933a85cd254a16dc3bfbbea2ef8d8f3","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"任游嘅綠隊同<br />\n徐綽希嘅啡隊都贏第一場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66432f56af0365f58d2c5d0d9cfb1b3416bf6c6c","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"綠隊3場全勝第一<br />\n啡隊排第2<br />\n幾大機會入4強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc75996f628253b48784d07d030633cb895f4290","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T13:26:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aN31r80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaN31r80.jpg&h=6bcc53a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來將冰場分開兩邊打3v3"},{"pid":"becaaa1e9ed94fc5a8a060f65616e4918256734c","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:43:23.000Z","msg":"<strong>任遊及徐綽希3人隊際冰球 雙雙殺入四強</strong><br />\n<br />\n在開幕禮任持旗手的冰球選手任遊及徐綽希，於混合奧委會3人隊際賽雙雙殺入4強，由於兩人屬不同隊伍，因此港隊篤定最少會有一面獎牌落袋。<br />\n<br />\n任遊效力的綠隊於小組賽7戰6勝1負，以首名躋身4強。而徐綽希效力的啡隊，則取得5勝2負次名出線。兩支隊伍將於4強分別迎戰黑隊及紅隊，力爭決賽席位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f537327f71efc52ec73cda453da9d5ffc7bd08","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T20:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wwe4AhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwwe4AhP.jpg&h=f63c48e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n綠隊反勝黑隊入決賽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n任游坐銀望金<br />\n徐綽希就爭銅牌"},{"pid":"f5c72e3fdbf6f0b76d40228a94603c2663694e74","tid":1810372,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78a1238317866fd8b6dec23377b9e64fc33c3a69","tid":1810372,"uid":5149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T14:57:18.000Z","msg":"金牌&amp;銅牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}